title.13: Peter Parker, the Spectacular Spider-Man Annual (1979) #7

description.0: The Impossible Man just wants a little fun - and he's terrorizing the New Mutants for that good time!
description.1: Star Brand is confronted by three mental hospital escapees, each with special powers...Mr. Lovejoy , Mrs. Kaminski and Deanie! Can Ken Connell take the three on? Or will he allow himself to be distracted by personal matters?
description.2: Thor deceived! His arm newly repaired by old friend Tony Stark, Thor clashes with several old foes, but unbeknownst to him, they're merely illusions, placed over innocent people? Who in Thor's life could possibly be responsible for such dark mischief (who else)?
description.5: Logan's training continues...and he's got his sights set on Sabretooth.
description.8: The FF assembles to take down dueling, intergalactic brothers Umbra and Jaguur. Can the team battle two enemies while two team members battle amongst themselves?
description.11: GANG WAR PART 1 Flash Thompson is still missing and Spider-Man's up to his webs with the super-powered crime claiming New York. And now a new threat emerges- the mysterious Blue Boys are adding their own brand of terror to the Gang Wars!
description.12: Captain America's former sidekick, Nomad, returns! And Captain America is faced with one of the most difficult decisions of his career when he learns Nomad is out to kill Miami's biggest drug dealer, the Slug!
description.13: It's off to the South of France for Peter and his blushing bride, Mary Jane, as they set off for a fun-filled, carefree honeymoon. But the trip takes an unexpected turn when Peter accepts an offer from none other than the Puma!
description.15: After three days in the field, the 4/23rd are allowed a brief respite before being sent back on patrol.
description.16: Old McDonald's Farm turns into a House of Horrors when Peter and the interns discover that Dr. Chickenstein is trying to create a vegetable monster!
description.19: The Wedding of Peter Parker and Mary Jane Watson!  'Nuff said!
description.21: What is the fate of the hunters if they cannot capture and return the D.P.7 to the Clinic?
description.22: Colossus takes center stage in ""Prison of the Heart!""
description.23: The kids of Psi-Force realize that they are stronger together than apart, and make a pact to stick together. In this issue? The psychic team goes to school for the very first time!
description.28: Thor battles the Marauders and makes his way toward Angel. Can he save the winged mutant, who has been brutally pinned to a wall with energy lances, or will Thor be the next defeated hero?
description.30: The West Coast Avengers may be out of Allatou's grasp…but now they've found themselves amongst the Cat People in a new, weird dimension!
description.33: The D.P.7 use their super powers to stay one step ahead of their pursuers.
description.34: Nightcrawler takes up one of Wolverine's challenges in ""The Big Dare!""
description.35: When you're a kid with superpowers, it always seems like someone is out to hurt you. And no one understands that struggle better than the agents of Psi-Force!
description.36: Matt Murdock is trying to settle into his new life where he's a diner cook by day and Daredevil by night, but Black Widow doesnt believe it's enough for Matt. An encounter with the sound manipulating villain known as Klaw, might prove Black Widow right!
description.37: It's the ultimate battle of Hulk vs. Hulk between Banner and Rick Jones!
description.38: If you thought the old Dominic Fortune was something, wait until you see the new Dominic Fortune. Plus, the mystery of Sabbath. Why must the truth stay hidden?
description.40: When a foreign dictator discovers that Kenneth Connell possesses the Star Brand, the world had better watch out! The dictator will stop at nothing in his quest for the most dangerous weapon in the universe!
description.44: The White House receives warning of the sun's impending instability. But the sun's not the only thing heating up- Johnny and Alicia get engaged!
description.50: PFC Ed Marks heads to Vietnam straight from basic training, and learns about the true horrors of war firsthand.
description.51: While looking for Flash Thompson, Spidey runs into villainess Titania mid heist. And she's called in backup from her fianc', Carl "The Crusher" Creel! How will Spider-Man defeat Titania and Absorbing Man when civilian life's at risk? Time to call in the Avengers!
description.52: With the merciless Masters of Evil on the rampage, the new Whirlwind and Trapster plot to deliver to the team the greatest prize of all- Captain America's head!
description.57: Circumstances become dire for the team when a mutant at the local high school commits suicide after being bullied. The New Mutants reflect, and urge the community to understand the impact of their words.
description.59: Tigra's personal trauma threatens to wreck not only her life, but that of her fellow West Coast Avengers as well! Will Hellcat and her husband Daimon Hellstrom be able to help her before Master Pandemonium makes things worse?
description.61: Is Spider-Man a mutant? Publisher J. Jonah Jameson hires the mutant-hunting X-Factor to find out!
description.62: Over the last few issues, Captain America's faith in the American dream suffered its greatest blow- he'd been forced to take a life! Can Cap's faith be renewed after what he has just experienced? Introducing the incredible Super Patriot!
description.63: The Black Widow enlists Daredevils help in tracking a rogue super solider.
description.64: Mysterious happenings persist at the Gamma Base after Bruce Banner is thought to be cured. Meanwhile, the Grey Hulk takes a hostage...
description.65: Iron Man faces his cruelest foe yet...Ironmonger! Guest-starring the dashing hero of the Thirties: Dominic Fortune!
description.66: Star Brand meets Spitfire and the Troubleshooters in an attempt to save a little boy in a well! Meanwhile, does Ken have enough confidence in his new powers to defeat cruise ship terrorists in the Middle East?
description.70: Reed, Sue and Johnny travel to Monster Isle to settle team tension. The excursion culminates in a shocking twist however, when they discover that a former teammate is working for the Mole Man!
description.73: Nothing goes to plan at the Cheese Queen Beauty Pageant in Hockawottamie, Wisconsin…including who takes first place!
description.79: When seven super-powered individuals escape the Clinic, the hunt is on!
description.80: The X-Men grieve the death of Thunderbird in ""Mourning!""
description.81: A New Universe series starts here! Working for the CIA is a gift and a curse, especially when your job is to find living, breathing psychic kids!
description.82: The West Coast Avengers face four foes even the Avengers wouldn't think about fighting, because these guys control the forces that bind the universe!
description.83: It's Iron Man vs. X-Factor! But will the two should-be allies be able to put aside their difference in time to stop a reality-altering threat?
description.86: Legion is overcome by his many conflicting personalities, ultimately rendering Wolfsbane and Moira MacTaggert unconscious!
description.87: Zaniac is en route to kill Jane Foster! Justin Peace finds out he is too late! Will Thor be able to figure out Peace's true intentions and save Jane in time? Or will he be late as well?
description.89: An encounter with Mr. Hyde leaves Matt Murdock to remember the past and how he became Daredevil.
description.90: S.H.I.E.L.D. creates a genetic bath that will allow Bruce Banner to control the Hulk. But when the Hulk and Rick Jones are thrown in the bath by accident, a new Hulk emerges!
description.91: The Living Laser has lost his corporeal form and is now a "living" creature of laser energy. Stark offers to help the Laser get his body back, but will the villain's pride prove too much?
description.92: Mechanic Ken Connell's whole life is changed when he receives the STAR BRAND- a brand granting the wearer infinite powers based off his imagination's allowance! Will Ken use his new powers for good or for evil?
description.95: The team joins Wyatt Wingfoot to free She-Hulk and destroy the alternate Central City. Meanwhile, Reed sets a plan in motion to find Ben Grimm!
description.98: The super-powered Sinister Syndicate has both Spider-Man and Silver Sable trapped on Coney Island! Who'll be left to pick up the pieces?
description.99: Captain America's personal war against the anarchy champion, Flag-smasher, leads Cap straight into on Alpine ambush in "The Chasm."

4.text: Tabitha Smith (AKA Boom-Boom) returns much to the amusement (and terror) of the X-Factor crew!

9.text: While Wolverine battles Sabretooth in the Mansion, Malice takes complete control of Dazzler and reveals her mutant identity to the public. Can the X-Men extract vital information from Creed while he battles Wolverine? Can Dazzler fight off Malice?

14.text: It's anything but Eden in "The Garden" where the Morituri recruits undergo harsh tests designed to develop their powers, or kill them. Meanwhile, during their harsh training, the alien horde ravaging of the Earth increases.

19.text: The wedding of Peter Parker and Mary Jane Watson! 'Nuff said!

20.text: Moon Knight versus a frightening elemental power!

24.text: With Teddy as his “real-world anchor”, Keith takes on the task of helping an old friend overcome drug addiction.

26.text: Wicket and Teebo must rescue Princess Kneesaa, who has been shrunken by the Fleebogs in order to defeat the ra-lugg. Little does she know that she will continue to shrink unless Wicket and Teebo reach her in time!

27.text: Featuring the malevolent Doctor Doom! Cloak and Dagger must prevent Doom from eliminating all nuclear power worldwide.

28.text: Thor battles the Marauders and makes his way toward Angel. Can he save the winged mutant, who has been brutally pinned to a wall with energy lances, or will Thor be the next defeated hero?
Thor battles the Marauders and makes his way toward Angel. Can he save the winged mutant, who has been brutally pinned to a wall with energy lances, or will Thor be the next defeated hero?

29.text: Spider-Man gets involved in AVENGERS: UNDER SIEGE. Featuring Doctor Doom and the Hobgoblin!
Spider-Man gets involved in AVENGERS: UNDER SIEGE. Featuring Doctor Doom and the Hobgoblin!

30.text: The West Coast Avengers may be out of Allatou's grasp…but now they've found themselves amongst the Cat People in a new, weird dimension!

31.text: This may be the end of the road for Stephen Strange. Nearly killed in battle, the Sorcerer Supreme is now fading fast on an operating table…and without the assistance of his mystic powers. Is mortal medicine the only cure for Doctor Strange? An out-of-body experience may yield answers- answers that involve Sara Wolfe!

39.text: X-Factor takes on Harpoon and Arclight! But when several members of X-Factor are injured, leaving only Marvel Girl and Iceman to battle the Marauders, Angel must save a missing Morlock. One mutant will pay the ultimate price...

42.text: X-Factor learns that the Tunnelers and Drain Dwellers are not to be trusted.

47.text: What happends when C-3PO and R2D2 get seperated?

48.text: Power Pack heads down to the Morlock Tunnels to investigate. But investigating won't be all that they do, especially when they're attacked by Sabretooth!

49.text: The Earth of the near future has been invaded by aliens. Only one force is strong enough to confront them. Strike-Force Morituri! With normal citizens volunteering to become super heroes, what tolls will be paid for this new power?

53.text: The Kleinmann Institute sends out new agents to take out Keith. As Nightmask, Keith helps an influential physician overcome his suicidal thoughts.

54.text: In Switzerland, Dakota and Amos finally make contact with Ricky -- only to be captured by a Sheik who's after the nerve gas!

56.text: Top Dog’s Brainstorm Computer is acting all kinds of out of whack!

57.text: Circumstances become dire for the team when a mutant at the local high school commits suicide after being bullied. The New Mutants reflect, and urge the community to understand the impact of their words.

58.text: Thor heads down into the  Morlock Tunnels to provide assistance. When he arrives he is attacked by Blockbuster, Harpoon, and Vertigo. Will the God of Thunder defeat them in time, so that he may aid his allies?

59.text: Tigra's personal trauma threatens to wreck not only her life, but that of her fellow West Coast Avengers as well! Will Hellcat and her husband Daimon Hellstrom be able to help her before Master Pandemonium makes things worse?

60.text: DIVIDED WE FALL! The Masters of Evil have claimed The Avengers Mansion as their own! What will happen to The Earth's Mightiest when they return to their HQ? The Black Knight is about to find out!
DIVIDED WE FALL! The Masters of Evil have claimed The Avengers Mansion as their own! What will happen to The Earth's Mightiest when they return to their HQ? The Black Knight is about to find out!

63.text: The Black Widow enlists Daredevil's help in tracking a rogue Super-Solider.

68.text: The team must contend with a mutant massacre in the Morlock Tunnels.

71.text: The Marauders have begun to exterminate the Morlocks in the abandoned subway tunnels beneath New York. After, a injured Morlock escapes and makes his way to the Mansion to enlist the X-Men's help. Prepare for the X-Men vs. Riptide!

74.text: Marvel's New Universe! Following a bizarre astronomical event, teenage Keith Remsen comes out of a coma with the extraordinary ability to enter other’s dreams! Even stranger, a few weeks prior he was a target for assassination! Now, Keith, along with his sister Teddy must uncover who killed their parents and what secrets are being kept under wraps at a shadowy dream research institute!

76.text: Can the Ewoks triumph over the Demons of Endor?

77.text: THE SHOW MUST GO ON! Dagger decides to join a circus, but eventually snaps out of it and rejoins Cloak and Bill to track a drug ring to its supply source.

78.text: The Incredible Hulk is lulled into a stupor by a talented ‘medicine man’. But the calm soon subsides when Hammer & Anvil attack!

82.text: The West Coast Avengers face four foes even the Avengers wouldn't think about fighting, because these guys control the forces that bind the universe!

83.text: It's Iron Man vs. X-Factor! But will the two should-be allies be able to put aside their difference in time to stop a reality-altering threat?

84.text: Morgana Blessing, Sorcerer Supreme? Defeated in demonic battle, Doctor Strange lies injured and powerless. Yet somehow, his mystic abilities have merged with Morgana! The Sanctum Santorum is nearly razed. Will Morgana embrace black magic?

85.text: RITES OF CONQUEST! Baron Zemo is hell bent on destroying the Avengers once and for all! The Masters of Evil have stormed The Avengers Mansion and there's only one person home: Jarvis!
RITES OF CONQUEST! Baron Zemo is hell bent on destroying the Avengers once and for all! The Masters of Evil have stormed The Avengers Mansion and there's only one person home: Jarvis!

86.text: Legion is overcome by his many conflicting personalities, ultimately rendering Wolfsbane and Moira MacTaggert unconscious!

87.text: Zaniac is en route to kill Jane Foster! Justin Peace finds out he is too late! Will Thor be able to figure out Peace's true intentions and save Jane in time? Or will he be late as well?
Zaniac is en route to kill Jane Foster! Justin Peace finds out he is too late! Will Thor be able to figure out Peace's true intentions and save Jane in time? Or will he be late as well?

88.text: Atlantis is under the thrall of the warlord Attuma! Namor the Sub-Mariner, the rightful ruler of Atlantis, recruits Alpha Flight to help him take it back! And they'll have help doing it, from none other than Earth's Mightiest heroes, the Avengers!

94.text: Rusty and Skids try to avoid being captured by another mutant team - Freedom Force!
